Usage: COLOR event color1 color2 color3 color4 color5
  Sets colors for events

  Available events are WARNING, JOIN, MSG, NOTICE, NETSPLIT, INVITE,
  MODE, SETTING, HELP, LEAVE, NOTIFY, CTCP, KICK, DCC, WHO, WHOIS,
  PUBLIC, CDCC, LINKS, DCCCHAT, CSCAN, COLNICK, COLME, COLMISC, 
  COLSBAR1 and COLSBAR2.
  
  Available colors are BOLD, UNDERLINE, FLASH, REVERSE, BLACK, RED,
  GREEN, YELLOW, BLUE, PURPLE, CYAN and WHITE. You can also set
  background colors by appending BG to color name (example : REDBG).
  You can combine colors together, use comma to separate them
  (example : BOLD,YELLOW).
